name: name-game
description: Leading scientists have proven, via science, that learning your coworkers names while starting a new job is useful. Your test project is to make it happen! We have a simple version hosted at [namegame.willowtreemobile.com](http://namegame.willowtreemobile.com/) which you can test. The api is located at [https://willowtreeapps.com/api/v1.0/profiles/](https://willowtreeapps.com/api/v1.0/profiles/).
